---
import SiteLayout from '@/layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="About" description="About Sasha Vinčić: AI engineering leader, software engineer, founder, and workshop facilitator.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5 py-20 md:py-28">
    <p class="mb-5 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-base-500">About</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-6xl font-light leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-7xl">Software engineer. AI pragmatist. Builder of things that need to work.</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg mt-12 max-w-none prose-a:text-base-950 prose-a:underline hover:prose-a:text-base-700">
      <p>I am Sasha Vinčić, based in Malmö, Sweden. I have spent more than 25 years building software, leading technical work, starting companies, advising teams, and trying to keep technology useful instead of theatrical.</p>
      <p>Today my work sits mostly around AI-assisted engineering, product development, and technical leadership. I help teams move from impressive demos to systems people can actually use, maintain, and trust.</p>
      <p>I am connected to Valentine Web Systems, Eletive, workshops around agentic engineering, and a set of practical AI experiments under the Digital Viking name. This site is the personal one: the place for my work, writing, background, and ways to get in touch.</p>
      <p>If you want exact LinkedIn-style credentials here, paste the profile text and I will make it sharper. The current version uses public snippets and conservative wording rather than inventing a résumé.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
